{"tid":1959572,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"如果下年第三次世界大戰， 宜家有咩可以準備","createTime":"2020-04-05T13:21:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-05T22:54:59.000Z","uid":78645,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a54e7f62c730b4ad3e8601a5526f344d71145f95","tid":1959572,"uid":78645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T13:21:12.000Z","msg":"午餐肉？"},{"pid":"957138a495bdb4769a5bed7f17063239ff1d86a9","tid":1959572,"uid":177089,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T13:23:57.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎又好，三戰又好，UFO又好,有咩事發生都唔驚，要鳩縮唔出街都實有得食~~<br />\n當然，到有日真係出現 <br />\n全香港範圍MAP炮 就咩都唔使<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LYVjojj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLYVjojj.jpg&h=795a3679&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n放在廚房櫃的鑵頭同米 <br />\n（現鑵頭總存貨有$10000左右）<br />\n米有50kg<br />\n由歐洲火腿，到荷美爾午餐肉、回鍋肉、豆、菜、金寶湯<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0V2t056.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0V2t056.jpg&h=ae19cc75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一箱箱未開太多，放到出廳（依d全部係魚）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/amP0ScO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FamP0ScO.jpg&h=ded221dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n水污染，未驚~~~現有16箱 1.5L X12<br />\n其實一向飲樽裝水好耐，現在D水喉水煮完都飲到唔舒服<br />\n即食面 有 5箱左右啦...<br />\n<br />\n另外，打邊爐石油氣有存貨 21支...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n來吧~~~<br />\n大混亂~~~<br />\n社區爆發~~~<br />\n無水~~無電~~無野買的日子呀~~~<br />\n<br />\n期待，手持午餐肉就可以有西屌的日子<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3da2ce1b70007a16c69b492a0debad84cbba932","tid":1959572,"uid":42734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2